Census Data Tables

The tables below show stats in cells where columns and rows meet, like a spreadsheet. Tables can be by subject, or in rank order, or made the way you want them. You can download many tables in XLS, CSV and PDF formats.

In data.census.gov , you can modify tables, add/remove geographies, print, download, create a map, and view notes.
